CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season"
TitMainTitle: Men, and women, possibly including Phyllis Pitts wearing plaid skirt on left, seated at picnic tables in pavilion with Chinese paper lanterns overhead, at Lovuola's Farm for Junior Mothers night picnic during FROGS week
